b'Your career'
b'Knowledge of\xc2\xa0adaptive technology support for\xc2\xa0people with disabilities is beneficial to any field. With advances in technology providing support for\xc2\xa0people with disabilities to live more independently in the community, the demand for these professionals will continue to grow.'
b'A certificate in assistive technology is a perfect fit if you serve individuals in:'
